Code.Terraform:
```hcl
resource "google_bigquery_dataset" "<example_resource_name>" {
  dataset_id = "<example_resource_id>"
  location   = "<LOCATION>"

  # Critical: apply CMEK at the dataset level so the check passes
  default_encryption_configuration {
    kms_key_name = "projects/<KMS_PROJECT_ID>/locations/<LOCATION>/keyRings/<KEY_RING>/cryptoKeys/<KEY_NAME>" # Critical: sets CMEK
  }
}
```
